are out of pity

212
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:21,740
or guilt?

213
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:22,740
Rong Xia!

214
00:12:23,260 --> 00:12:23,860
I

215
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:27,020
